UPCOMING CLIPS GENERATOR — computes the next N clips the 24/7 queue
will attempt to generate, so Vigge can see what's about to land
and decide whether to pause/reorder.

Uses the same iteration order as wan21_24_7_queue.py:
  for scene_idx in scenes:
    for img_idx in images:
      for char in chars:
        combo = (char, img_idx, scene_idx)

